'''希林·伊巴迪'''（{{lang-fa|{{big|شيرين عبادى}}}}，''Širin Ebādi''，{{lang|en|'''Shirin Ebadi'''}}，{{bd|1947年|6月21日|catIdx=E}}）是一位[[伊朗|伊朗]]女性[[律师|律师]]和人权活动者，{{link-en|人权捍卫者中心|Defenders of Human Rights Center}}的创始人。2003年10月10日因她为[[民主|民主]]和[[人权|人权]]，特别是为[[婦女權利|妇女]]和[[儿童|儿童]]的权益和[[庇護權|庇護權]]所作出的努力而被授予[[诺贝尔和平奖|诺贝尔和平奖]]，成为第一位获奖的伊朗人和穆斯林女性。

2009年11月26日希林·伊巴迪突遭伊朗政府強制沒收其[[諾貝爾和平獎|諾貝爾和平獎]]，該舉動是諾貝爾和平獎頒發以來從未有的事，顯示伊朗政府打擊反對言論的人士。<ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/news/world/middle_east/article6934015.ece| work=TIMESONLINE| title=Iran seizes Nobel winner Shirin Edabi’s medal| date=2009-11-27| accessdate=2009-11-27| archive-date=2011-07-15| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110715232700/http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/news/world/middle_east/article6934015.ece| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Iran Denies It Confiscated Ebadi's Nobel Medal">{{cite news|author=Reuters|url=http://www.nytimes.com/reuters/2009/11/27/world/international-uk-norway-iran-nobel.html|title=Iran Denies It Confiscated Ebadi's Nobel Medal|date=2009-11-27|accessdate=2009-11-27|work=The New York Times}}{{Dead link}}</ref><ref>[http://www.reuters.com/article/latestCrisis/idUSGEE5AP1X5 Norway says Iran confiscated Ebadi's Nobel] {{Wayback|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/latestCrisis/idUSGEE5AP1X5 |date=20210125061354 }} [[Reuters|Reuters]] 27 November</ref>

伊巴迪在德黑兰居住，但由于伊朗对批评现行政权的公民迫害的增加，2009年6月以来她一直流亡在英国。<ref>[http://www.newsweek.com/id/229965 "Shirin Ebadi: The Activist in Exile"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.newsweek.com/id/229965 |date=20210303082455 }} ''[[Newsweek|Newsweek]]'' 30 March 2010</ref>2004年，她入选《[[福布斯|福布斯]]》杂志的“[[世界百名权威女性|世界百名权威女性]]”名单。<ref>[https://archive.is/20120730133811/http://www.forbes.com/finance/lists/11/2004/LIR.jhtml?passListId=11&passYear=2004&passListType=Person&uniqueId=POPA&datatype=Person Forbes.com: Forbes 100 Most Powerful Women in the World 2004]</ref>她还入选“100个最具影响力女性”名单。<ref>{{cite book|author=Britannica Educational Publishing|title=The 100 Most Influential Women of All Time|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=3gVvaAUcnq0C&pg=PA330|accessdate=2012-01-15|date=2009-10-01|publisher=The Rosen Publishing Group|isbn=978-1-61530-058-7|pages=330–331|archive-date=2017-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170427004318/https://books.google.com/books?id=3gVvaAUcnq0C&pg=PA330|dead-url=no}}</ref>

